---
title: Crispy Buffalo-Spiced Chicken with Blue Cheese Sauce, Sour Cream ’n’ Chive Mashed Potatoes & Roasted Carrots
description: Are you the type of person who only goes to sporting events because of the fact that buffalo wings may be present? We’re with you, and that’s why our chefs took the beloved dish from messy app to epic weeknight dinner. First, chicken is brushed with sour cream, then coated in a Frank’s Red Hot spiced panko mixture. It’s roasted to juicy, crunchy perfection, then drizzled with creamy flecked blue cheese sauce. Oh, and did we mention there’s roasted carrots and sour cream and chive mashed potatoes on the side?! Yeah, it’s safe to say this dish is a slam dunk.
